---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 17, 2026';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy policy" description="Let's Skate Foundation's privacy policy: what we collect, how we use it, and how to contact us about your data.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="sec-inner privacy">
      <div class="label"><span class="label-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Last updated: {lastUpdated}</div>
      <h1 class="heading">Privacy policy</h1>

      <p>
        Let's Skate Foundation ("LSF," "we," "our") is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit
        organization. EIN 99-4111339. This policy explains what we collect
        on letsskate.org, how we use it, and how to reach us about your data.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect the minimum we need to run the foundation, and nothing more.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact form submissions.</strong> If you write to us
          through the contact form, we receive your name, email address,
          and your message. These are forwarded to admin@letsskate.org.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Donations.</strong> When you donate, our payment
          processor Stripe collects your name, email, billing address,
          and payment information. We never see or store your card number.
          We retain donor records (name, email, mailing address, donation
          amount, and date) to issue IRS-required acknowledgment letters
          and for our own bookkeeping.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Basic analytics.</strong> We may use privacy-friendly
          analytics that count visits without tracking individuals or
          using cookies for advertising.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What we don't do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We don't sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing.</li>
        <li>We don't use advertising trackers or third-party advertising cookies.</li>
        <li>We don't build profiles of individual visitors.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Registration on Elmbrook Speedskating</h2>
      <p>
        Skating registration is handled by our partner platform at
        <a href="https://www.elmbrookspeedskating.org">elmbrookspeedskating.org</a>.
        That site has its own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing it
        before registering.
      </p>

      <h2>Donor records</h2>
      <p>
        We retain donor records for at least seven years to comply with
        IRS recordkeeping requirements. You can request a copy of your
        donation history or ask us to delete non-required data at any time
        by emailing
        <a href="mailto:admin@letsskate.org">admin@letsskate.org</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's data</h2>
      <p>
        letsskate.org is not directed at children, and we do not knowingly
        collect personal information from children under 13. Information
        about youth participants in our programs is collected only through
        the registration platform with parental consent, and is governed
        by that platform's privacy policy.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions, requests, or concerns? Email
        <a href="mailto:admin@letsskate.org">admin@letsskate.org</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy { max-width: 720px; }
  .privacy h1.heading { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
  .privacy h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  .privacy p, .privacy li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .privacy ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  .privacy a { color: var(--teal); font-weight: 700; }
  .privacy strong { color: var(--dark); }
</style>
